        "cooked": "<p>You can mod all the scenes, both outdoor and indoor with IdaJS. In this tutorial we only mod indoor scene, but the video also shows the storm Sample mod, where the outdoor scene is modified.</p>\n<p>To explore the existing LBA2 objects and scripts in the outdoor scene, you need to use another tool: LBA2Remake Editor. LBArchitect only helps to explore the indoor scenes.</p>",
